N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 8450.10 - Fees

State Regulations
(a) There shall be
no fee charged for: (1)
inspection of
records; (2)
search of records; or
(3)
any certification pursuant
to this Part. (b) The
fee for photocopies not exceeding 8 1/2 x 14 inches is 25 cents per
page. Notes
